      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to list my pride and joy. This car is in truly stunning condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and honestly looks like it belongs in a showroom! The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019ve taken extra care to keep it in tip-top shape, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. You\u2019ve really got to see this one in person to appreciate how perfect it is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
