    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This example reflects a strictly climate-controlled life, retaining original factory paint depth and a pristine interior free of bolster wear or UV degradation. Mechanically, the high-revving powerplant remains in peak form, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement using VAC coated bearings and updated throttle actuators to ensure total operational integrity. The 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains taut, showing no signs of subframe fatigue, and retains its factory-spec EDC (Electronic Damping Control) calibration. Every service interval has been meticulously documented with OE-spec lubricants. This is a turn-key collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
